title: The Wedding Present- Hit Parade Complete
description:
In 1992, The Wedding Present released a 7" every month, each making it into UK Top 30. This is a compilation of the 12 singles with their respective b-side. Also included is the bonus disc that came with the first 30 000 copies of Hit Parade 2, containing bbc session takes of all the a-sides.
 Hit Parade 3 is a french only release including "Rocket" (Boing! b-side) and 5 tracks that were previously unreleased at the time (the tracks have later been included in the Seamonsters Camden Deluxe release)
